{"tid":1700643,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］盛芳街公園有4架狗車捉左2位手足上車","createTime":"2019-11-08T15:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T18:27:57.000Z","uid":279181,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"0caff725b279785c707e9bf5f29870d9ef64126d","tid":1700643,"uid":279181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"大概10點45分個陣係盛芳街有4架狗車落車入公園捉左2位男手足上車<br />\n全程淨閃藍燈 無響聲<br />\n見到2隻便衣狗捉左啲手足上車<br />\n懷疑岩岩葵廣活動完左之後比人跟蹤<br />\n有手足影到相可唔可以報上黎 我個陣無影到<br />\n好彩我地有手足係呢邊食緊野 如果唔係應該又會被失蹤<br />\n捉人全程無5分鐘 捉完就開曬4架狗車走人<br />\n見到有手足影相同拍片 可唔可以放上黎？<br />\n求求你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8960fa70dffa8f1f345c5b758b6e3d6ecc81c628","tid":1700643,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0057bfe4b8b8ad080c955380a4c04e2649eda3ac","tid":1700643,"uid":279181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"P牌樓主推唔到 <br />\n好大件事 唔想有手足被失蹤"},{"pid":"795e3cc9cd1246f4f143345e7a6de1bc8dddd8f4","tid":1700643,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4dfebc533f4d33cbb262e61387a792eb34e77e04","tid":1700643,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c530fe505c6707c2be382972ed2430424546268e","tid":1700643,"uid":29555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bf7050ff329228ea7405c459e12a24c8359d199","tid":1700643,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1915a347ef43091c0bb00c7b190490aa17b6390","tid":1700643,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"753696ad8b42c789d30f016a03a0625eb156a5a7","tid":1700643,"uid":279181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy